When it comes to the inspiration brand, Cheryl Jackson is the one of the nation's leading media personalities in the industry. A 2X Stellar Award winner, she created the 1st Urban Inspiration Radio Station in the country. Each weekday, she hosts "Cheryl Jackson in the Midday" her highly rated radio show, heard on Praise 104.1 (Washington DC), Praise 106.1 (Baltimore,MD) and Worldwide on Urban One's Inspiration Network.

Introducing The Simplified Tax Resolution Podcast, a bi-weekly podcast discussing IRS debt resolution, retirement planning, accurate and affordable tax preparation, and more. This podcast is presented by Tax Biz USA, the premier tax agency focused on affordable tax resolution services for small businesses and individuals preparing for retirement.
I’m so excited to be partnering with @taxbizusa and hosting this show to make tax education fun and easy to understand. Be sure to listen & subscribe anywhere podcasts are available or by clicking the link in my bio.

It’s amazing how grief hits us in different ways.  It took me a minute to make this post because my cousin Renee’s passing has triggered moments of unexpected heavy grief. Growing up on Jefferson Street, we were raised like sisters.  Memories of those times floods my mind!  As kids me Renee and Tony “Bubble” did EVERYTHING together.  I was the baby of the bunch so growing up with them matured me!  They protected me and spoiled me rotten. I’ve got stories for days.  Jefferson Street was special!  You fought long and hard, rest well cousin! (Please kiss Grandma, Pop Poo, Bubble, Mommy and Daddy for me) #sistercousins #Nay #IhateMS #uptowngirls
